author: Madyyyyyys _ mess
text: And last I would say .. making art saved me in going through diff emotional turmoils. I kept making it and it SAVED me. Thankyou all who have always brought a smile on my face by appreciating it. Thankyou for the journey! What a ride!

author: Madyyyyyys _ mess
text: My take away from last yr is to have more empathy in me and around me and this past yr makes us a better human.We all will one day will pass but this belief pushes us to be a better self.

author: Madyyyyyys _ mess
text: During these times I have seen people died of viruses but also from the ugly incidents we have seen along like "Sialkot" and "Noor". What if the people who are still alive and are dead inside. I wish and pray that they get into a wellness journey too.

author: Madyyyyyys _ mess
text:
It made me understand my purpose of life? Why I do the things I do? 

I crossed paths with many people and learnt interesting,necessary and important lessons. Tried to pluck out the Fake at the right time and it helped me CHANGE.

author: Madyyyyyys _ mess
text: If you had a smooth sail it was our responsibility to lend a helping hand to those who needed it the most. It was a yr of spiritual awekening. I realised not all things matter in life but the thing that do, I must hold on to them. It helped me understand who I'm?

author: Madyyyyyys _ mess
text: Many of those we knew in 2021 didnot see 2022. Their radiant and beautiful souls would explode everyday but we don't have them now. 2021 has shed people like autumn leaves. It was not a yr of 365 days but for few 365 battles. If they survived? They r the real heroes.
